l.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ed76163c3341fa1822be88c9df09f42d739c3f","tid":1790264,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>好仔唔當差</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28b28f423ef80631e930d95f1eb16078152981a","tid":1790264,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"7.21元朗數百白衣人衝入港鐵站無差別襲擊市民，5個月後的今日市民仍歷歷在目，今午起在元朗Yoho Mall聚集，誓言要追究真相，然而下午4時許，防暴警員突然闖入元朗Yoho Mall驅散在場集會民眾，途人急忙走避，本來仍在營業的店舖亦紛紛落閘「避防暴」，警員撤離商場後才敢重新開店。<br />\n<br />\n在Yoho Mall某餐廳工作的S與W表示，早於下午2時許商場中庭開始有民眾聚集，當時集會十分和平，但突然有防暴警員無預警地由Yoho Mall二期商場跑進一期商場驅散民眾，「啲舖頭見到佢哋（警察）好似好驚咁，佢哋行到邊就落閘落到邊」。<br />\n<br />\n其後，防暴警員更一度在他們工作的餐廳外停留，當時餐廳內有不少食客正在進餐，「本身都冇事，佢哋聽到有防暴嚟到就好驚，搶住要埋單走人」。為了保障食客安全，餐廳無奈下亦拉閘暫停營業。即使防暴警員撤離商場，但仍只有部份店舖重新營業。<br />\n<br />\nS與W透露，商場方面曾提醒店舖今日有集會舉行，商店可自行決定關門與否。<br />\nS與W均認為，警方闖入商場此舉十分無謂，因集會非常和平，途人亦如常地逛街購物，警員無必要特意進入商場內製造混亂，她們更指警員曾多次開咪向民眾大叫「你哋班暴徒」，質疑「佢哋似係想恐嚇人多過驅散」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191221/large/1576926880_6e24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191221%2Flarge%2F1576926880_6e24.jpg&h=8dfa0413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191221/60403993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191221%2F60403993&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=48b3d182\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191221%2F60403993&h=8e4dab00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191221/60403993</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>當差正POK GUY</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35474f7f36de26f1d0c1d56e808ee0bbdec1df1","tid":1790264,"uid":13644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fogi8NB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffogi8NB.jpg&h=79bd8ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葉問有癌症死了！！<br />\n<br />\n葉問個仔學校打交被趕出校，佢自己又確診cancer<br />\n飛去美國幫仔搵學校，華人受歧視欺凌，葉問制止欺凌，得罪美軍陸戰隊軍官。李小龍美國出書、收鬼佬徙弟教功夫，引起唐人街華人武術界不滿。李小龍有美軍徒弟想將詠春引入部隊，受空手道教官打壓，派人去唐人街踢館，被葉問狠狠教訓。美國軍官同時派人打傷大量唐人街武師，搵移民局拉人。最後葉問入軍營挑機，打贏軍官。最後放棄個仔留學計劃，親自教個仔詠春。最後病發身亡。"},{"pid":"903cdb2b654bfed11d46e407b1c36f96060e7a5e","tid":1790264,"uid":22531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnBviCy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnBviCy.png&h=a96e4e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部9ho機bug左，前後9抽8隻7星<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499fb08d43a904cfea7e966aeb9a418e95c6c18d","tid":1790264,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"903cdb2b654bfed11d46e407b1c36f96060e7a5e","tid":1790264,"uid":22531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnBviCy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnBviCy.png&h=a96e4e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部9ho機bug左，前後9抽8隻7星<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:45:39.000Z","msg":"WUFFL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f792a375c6104a208d3f81211694df7518e7938e","tid":1790264,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】牛頭角警署懷疑被人投擲汽油彈，牆身亦被塗鴉。 <br />\n<br />\n有人用白色噴漆在警署外牆寫上「未敢忘記」四個大字，有清潔工人清理，外牆及地下都被熏黑，懷疑曾被人投擲汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n早上七時許，警方接報兆業街1號牛頭角警署懷疑遭縱火，警員及消防到場調查，檢獲玻璃碎片、2罐電油、4支打邊爐的石油氣樽。<br />\n<br />\n案件列作縱火及刑事毀壞，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374218&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374218%26refer%3DShare&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=1aacee1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374218%26refer%3DShare&h=b3392a08\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374218&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n教科書式快閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8dff9c2bab19a0173f573152692cf0748c652a2","tid":1790264,"uid":15567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f792a375c6104a208d3f81211694df7518e7938e","tid":1790264,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】牛頭角警署懷疑被人投擲汽油彈，牆身亦被塗鴉。 <br />\n<br />\n有人用白色噴漆在警署外牆寫上「未敢忘記」四個大字，有清潔工人清理，外牆及地下都被熏黑，懷疑曾被人投擲汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n早上七時許，警方接報兆業街1號牛頭角警署懷疑遭縱火，警員及消防到場調查，檢獲玻璃碎片、2罐電油、4支打邊爐的石油氣樽。<br />\n<br />\n案件列作縱火及刑事毀壞，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374218&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374218%26refer%3DShare&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=1aacee1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2F